               <msContents>
                  <msItem>
                     <p> Tomas, son of <persName>
                           <forename>Richard</forename> de <surname>Cucheneia</surname>
                        </persName>, gives to 
                  Ailiva and to his youngest surviving
                  daughter by her, the land which her father held by the service of one bovate,
                  together with Reginald her brother, and the land which he also held by the service of
                  one bovate, to hold <pb n="275"/> of the <orgName key="org_103022">hospital of Jerusalem</orgName> of which the said
                  Thomas was a brother at a rent of 12d. until his return from the Holy Sepulchre, and if
                  he does not return, for 2s. annual rent, for his soul and for the souls of his father and mother. 
                  (<origDate notBefore="1170" notAfter="1180" precision="low">c. 1170-1180</origDate>.)
                  . </p>
